    <a href="https://ebible.org/eng-web/ROM14.htm" target="_blank">Romans 14</a>
  </li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>New Creation Reality</h2>
<p>
New Creation communities are not built on hype.
They are built on faithfulness, responsibility, and peace.
</p>

<p>
Christ’s reign does not remove us from ordinary life.
It restores order within it.
</p>

<hr />

<h2>Reflection</h2>
<p>
Where might I be tempted to confuse spiritual expectation
with avoidance of responsibility?
</p>

